Package: EricksenLeslie
Version: 0.11
Date: 2008-07-08
Title: numerical solution of Ericsken-Leslie equations for 1D liquid crystal cells
Author: Steph Cornford <eltadcirad@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Steph Cornford <eltadcirad@gmail.com>
Suggests: uniaxialOptics
Description: A 1D finite volume model of the
	Ericksen-Leslie equations for nematic liquid crytsals.
	Includes pressure driven flow, flexoelectricity, 
        ion drift-diffusion equations.
License: GPL (>=2)
URL: http://r-forge.r-project.org/projects/photonics/
